---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="wrapper container mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-body">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your data when you use this website. By using the site, you consent to the practices described below.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">a. Automatically Collected Data</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      When you visit our website, certain information is automatically collected for operational and analytical purposes:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">IP Address:</span> Collected by our web server (NGINX) for security and traffic analysis. This data is stored temporarily and is not used for tracking.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">Analytics Data:</span> We use Google Analytics to collect anonymized information about your interactions with the site, including pages viewed, time spent, and other usage statistics.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">b. Voluntarily Provided Data</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you contact us via email, we may collect the following information:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">Email Address:</span> Provided by you when sending an email. This information will only be used to respond to your inquiry and will not be shared.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">Message Content:</span> Any additional information you voluntarily include in your email.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        To monitor and improve the performance of the website.
      </li>
      <li>
        To respond to inquiries sent via email.
      </li>
      <li>
        To ensure the security and reliability of the website.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We do not share your personal information with third parties, except for the following:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">Google Analytics:</span> Anonymized usage data is shared with Google for analytical purposes. You can review Google’s privacy policies here:
        <a
          href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
          class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 visited:text-purple-600"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Google Privacy Policy
        </a>.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">4. Managing Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You have the right to manage your data. For analytics, you can manage your cookie preferences using the button on the bottom left corner of this site. If you wish to delete or inquire about any data we may hold, please contact us at:
      <a
        href="mailto:artnikkila@gmail.com"
        class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 visited:text-purple-600"
      >
        artnikkila@gmail.com
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        <ul class="list-disc mb-4">
      <li>IP Address Data: Stored temporarily by our server logs and deleted automatically.</li>
      <li>Google Analytics Data**: Retained according to Google’s data retention policies.</li>
      <li>Email Data**: Retained only as long as necessary to respond to inquiries.</li>
    </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for legal reasons. Please revisit this page periodically to stay informed about how we handle your data.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm mt-8 text-gray-600">
      Last updated: <span class="font-semibold">24.11.2024</span>
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
